Package: mark-core-v2-frontend
Version: 0.1.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: CranckThatFranck <franck.oliver@outlook.com.br>
Depends: python3.12, python3.12-venv, python3-tk
Description: Minimal desktop frontend for Mark Core v2
 A minimal Linux desktop client for the Mark Core v2 backend.
 It connects to the backend through the existing WebSocket v2 protocol,
 shows sync_state, history, provider/model state, and can execute tasks.
